'''2015年歐爾金和諧號劫持案'''，是指一起發生於2015年6月11日至19日，8名{{link-en|印尼海盜|Piracy in Indonesia}}劫持了一艘[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]籍[[液貨船|油輪]]'''[[歐爾金和諧號|歐爾金和諧號]]'''（Orkim Harmony），最後在[[澳大利亚皇家空军|澳大利亚皇家空军]]、[[马来西亚皇家海军|马来西亚皇家海军]]、[[马来西亚皇家空军|马来西亚皇家空军]]、{{link-en|馬來西亞海事執法局|Malaysian Maritime Enforcement Agency}}、{{link-en|越南邊防隊|Vietnam Border Defense Force}}、[[越南海洋警察司令部|越南海洋警察司令部]]、[[印尼海軍|印尼海軍]]、[[泰國皇家海軍|泰國皇家海軍]]等單位的通力合作下，人質在[[南中國海|南中國海]]附近平安獲釋，油輪恢復航行的事件<ref name="id help"/><ref name="id join"/><ref name="au"/><ref name="first time"/><ref name="vss">{{cite web|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/crime/597816/vietnam-holds-tanker-hijackers|title=Vietnam holds tanker hijackers|publisher=[[Bangkok_Post|Bangkok Post]]|date=19 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015}}</ref>。
== 背景 ==
在歐爾金和諧號被劫持前的6月4日，另一艘油輪歐爾金勝利號（MT Orkim Victory），也曾在南中國海遭到8名手持兩把[[手槍|手槍]]與{{link-en|巴朗刀|Parang (knife)}}的印尼海盜劫持。勝利號在鄰近馬來西亞[[澳島|澳島]]約12.2[[海里|海里]]處遭到洗劫，在被釋放之前，勝利號被抽走了770[[公噸|公噸]]的[[柴油|柴油]]到另一艘船上；而海盜破壞了油輪上的所有[[通信|通信]]設備，並搶走了所有船員們的個人財物後逃之夭夭<ref>{{cite web|title=Hijacked oil tanker Orkim Harmony released as pirates flee off Malaysia coast|url=http://www.dw.com/en/hijacked-oil-tanker-orkim-harmony-released-as-pirates-flee-off-malaysia-coast/a-18526228|publisher=[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]]|accessdate=22 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626114755/http://www.dw.com/en/hijacked-oil-tanker-orkim-harmony-released-as-pirates-flee-off-malaysia-coast/a-18526228|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/06/14/Najib-Orkim-Harmony/|title=Najib anxious over disappearance of oil tanker|author=Nicholas Cheng|publisher=The Star|date=14 June 2015|accessdate=22 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626122741/http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/06/14/Najib-Orkim-Harmony/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 劫持 ==
歐爾金和諧號是在[[马来西亚标准时间|马来西亚标准时间]]（[[UTC+8|UTC+8]]）6月11日下午8時54分失聯的，當時它從[[马六甲|马六甲]]出發，預定往{{link-en|关丹港|Kuantan Port}}，正航行至{{coord|2|8.90|N|104|27.30|E|display=inline}}，即[[柔佛州|柔佛州]][[哥打丁宜縣|哥打丁宜縣]]丹絨素里里（Tanjung Sedili）附近水域<ref name="idp"/><ref name="ohn">{{cite web|url=http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/orkim-harmony-navy-widens-search-area-missing-oil-tanker-62621|title=Orkim Harmony: Navy widens search area for missing oil tanker|work=Bernama|publisher=Astro Awani|date=15 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626104737/http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/orkim-harmony-navy-widens-search-area-missing-oil-tanker-62621|dead-url=no}}</ref>。被劫持期間，有22名船員在船上，包括了16名[[馬來西亞人|馬來西亞人]]，5名[[印尼人|印尼人]]，與一名[[緬甸|緬甸]]籍公民<ref name="cna">{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/missing-oil-tanker/1917486.html|title=Missing oil tanker probably hijacked by pirates: Malaysian maritime police|author=Melissa Goh|publisher=[[Channel_News_Asia|Channel News Asia]]|date=15 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626131833/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/missing-oil-tanker/1917486.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。船上當時載有6000[[公噸|公噸]]的[[汽油|汽油]]，價值2100萬[[馬來西亞令吉|馬來西亞令吉]]（約合560萬[[美金|美金]]）<ref name="cna"/>，8名海盜都帶有手槍和帕兰刀<ref name="idp"/><ref name="nv"/>。

== 搜索行動 ==
6月12日起，{{link-en|馬來西亞海事執法局|Malaysian Maritime Enforcement Agency}}（Malaysian Maritime Enforcement Agency，縮寫：MMEA）開始在這艘油輪周邊的南中國海水域，搜尋這艘船的下落，範圍達到5萬[[平方公里|平方公里]]，因為這艘船已經失聯超過了10小時。馬來西亞當局認為，油輪可能被劫持至印尼的[[納土納群島|納土納群島]]和[[阿南巴斯群島|阿南巴斯群島]]附近<ref name="cna"/>；6月17日，一架自[[槟城|槟城]]州北方{{link-en|北海空军基地|RMAF Butterworth}}起飛的[[澳大利亚皇家空军|澳大利亚皇家空军]]{{link-en|洛克希德AP-3C型獵戶座海上巡邏機|Lockheed AP-3C Orion}}，在[[泰國灣|泰國灣]]的[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]與[[越南|越南]]的海上邊界處發現了它。根據其說法，油輪被重新粉刷，由藍色變成黑色，還被改名為「金哈蒙」（Kim Harmon）<ref name="au"/><ref name="first time"/><ref name="vss"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/missing-mt-orkim-harmony-cambodian-waters-renamed-and-repainted-62875|title=Missing MT Orkim Harmony in Cambodian waters, renamed and repainted|author=Abdul Hakim Rahman|publisher=Astro Awani|date=18 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626111759/http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/missing-mt-orkim-harmony-cambodian-waters-renamed-and-repainted-62875|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然[[柬埔寨皇家海軍|柬埔寨皇家海軍]]無法證實這項報告，不過給了馬來西亞在柬埔寨水域的聯合追蹤攔截油輪的行動開了綠燈<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.khmertimeskh.com/news/12399/hijacked-oil-tanker-tracked-in-cambodia-waters/|title=Hijacked Oil Tanker Tracked in Cambodia Waters|author=Jack Laurenson|publisher=Khmer Times|date=18 June 2015|accessdate=20 June 2015}}</ref>；隨後MMEA聯繫了[[越南海洋警察司令部|越南海洋警察司令部]]（VCG），告知此一消息；而VCG在接到消息後，也部署了兩艘巡邏船到該地區，[[印尼海軍|印尼海軍]]與[[泰國皇家海軍|泰國皇家海軍]]也都處於待命狀態。之後，VCG回報這艘船的位置在{{coord|9|21|N|102|44|E|display=inline}}，即[[富國島|富國島]]西南方約84海里處<ref name="info" group="附註">來源參見[[#外部連結|外部連結]]</ref>。

==後續==
在澳大利亞空軍回報之後，馬來西亞皇家海軍（RMN）和MMEA的艦艇就一直處於待命狀態，其後被部署到該區；6月19日，油輪在{{coord|9|10|N|103|10|E|display=inline}}被發現<ref name="info" group="附註"/>。船上的海盜央求马来西亚当局後撤五海浬（約9公里），讓他們能繼續其「旅程」至納土納群島<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/06/19/Orkim-Harmony-Natuna/|title=Tanker hijackers trying to escape to Indonesia's Natuna Island|publisher=The Star|date=19 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626135037/http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/06/19/Orkim-Harmony-Natuna/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，否则便要殺害船員<ref name="captured"/>。

經過一番交涉後，所有海盜搭上油轮上的[[救生艇|救生艇]]後逃脫。據油輪船長的說法，海盜當時威胁他，如果敢向馬來西亞當局洩漏他們的逃跑計畫，他們将对其家人不利<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/hijackers-threatened-to-go-after-crews-families-navy-chief-reveals|title=Hijackers threatened to go after crew’s families, navy chief reveals|author=Muzliza Mustafa|publisher=[[The_Malaysian_Insider|The Malaysian Insider]]|date=19 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619195251/http://www.themalaysianinsider.com/malaysia/article/hijackers-threatened-to-go-after-crews-families-navy-chief-reveals|archivedate=2015年6月19日}}</ref>。

馬來西亞時間凌晨2時30分，RMN和MMEA成功取得油輪，所有船員均平安，僅有一名人質被海盜開槍擊中他的左大腿，后被直升机送往医院<ref name="info" group="附註"/><ref name="injured"/><ref name="vcg">{{cite web|url=http://news.zing.vn/Canh-sat-VN-bat-8-ten-cuop-tau-dau-Malaysia-ra-sao-post551179.html|title=Cảnh sát VN bắt 8 tên cướp tàu dầu Malaysia ra sao?|language=vi|publisher=[[VNG_Corporation|Zing.vn]]|date=20 June 2015|accessdate=20 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626111359/http://news.zing.vn/Canh-sat-VN-bat-8-ten-cuop-tau-dau-Malaysia-ra-sao-post551179.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

數小時後，有8名疑似海盜的印尼人在[[土珠島|土珠島]]被捕，因為他們曾經和{{link-en|越南邊防隊|Vietnam Border Defense Force}}（VBDF）及VCG接觸過<ref name="vcg"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://tuoitre.vn/tin/the-gioi/20150619/vn-bat-giu-8-ten-cuop-bien-bo-chay-tu-tau-malaysia/763944.html|title=VN bắt giữ 8 tên cướp biển bỏ chạy từ tàu Malaysia|language=vi|publisher=[[Tuổi_Trẻ|Tuổi Trẻ]]|date=19 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619160645/http://tuoitre.vn/tin/the-gioi/20150619/vn-bat-giu-8-ten-cuop-bien-bo-chay-tu-tau-malaysia/763944.html|archive-date=2015-06-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，這些印尼人聲稱他們自己的漁船沉沒<ref name="vns"/><ref name="vss"/>；而MMEA立刻就此事，透過檢察長辦公室與[[馬來西亞外交部|外交部]]，向協助調查的[[越南政府|越南政府]]提出交涉，进行深入调查<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1465333|title=MMEA to investigate if 8 Indonesians linked to MT Orkim Harmony hijack|author=Bernard Cheah|publisher=[[The_Sun_(Malaysia)|The Sun]]|date=19 June 2015|accessdate=19 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619195026/http://www.thesundaily.my/news/1465333|dead-url=no}}</ref>。經由受傷的船員指認照片，確定這8人就是劫持油輪的海盜<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/orkim-harmony-eight-detained-confirmed-hijackers-63086|title=Orkim Harmony: Eight detained confirmed as hijackers|author=Abdul Hakim Rahman|publisher=Astro Awani|date=20 June 2015|accessdate=20 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626100214/http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/orkim-harmony-eight-detained-confirmed-hijackers-63086|dead-url=no}}</ref>；且在接受越南當局審訊期間，他們在看到經由馬來西亞當局提供的圖片與訊息後也坦承了<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/vietnam-says-8-indonesians-confess-hijacking-oil-tanker-035313218.html|title=Vietnam says 8 Indonesians confess to hijacking oil tanker|work=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|publisher=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]]|date=22 June 2015|accessdate=22 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622153618/http://news.yahoo.com/vietnam-says-8-indonesians-confess-hijacking-oil-tanker-035313218.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

馬來西亞时任首相[[纳吉·阿都拉萨|纳吉·阿都拉萨]]和时任內政部長[[阿末扎希|阿末扎希]]感謝所有參與及協助找回油輪，與讓22名船員獲釋，並逮捕海盜的各方單位，他們並向越南與印尼正式遞交引渡劫船者到馬來西亞的請求<ref name="accomplished"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/orkim-harmony-malaysia-request-extradition-suspected-hijackers-63091|title=Orkim Harmony: Malaysia to request extradition of suspected hijackers|work=Bernama|publisher=Astro Awani|date=20 June 2015|accessdate=20 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626103411/http://english.astroawani.com/malaysia-news/orkim-harmony-malaysia-request-extradition-suspected-hijackers-63091|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

越南當局進一步調查的結論是，基於這些罪犯能夠避開[[自動識別系統|自動識別系統]]（AIS）而未被發現，進而實施犯罪，表示他們經驗豐富，並非「業餘人士」；且VBDF和VCG在拘留他們時，也在救生艇中發現被藏入[[現金|現金]]。MMEA的調查還顯示，另外還有5人也參與了劫船，故總數可能達到13人。這些人使用[[拖船|拖船]]接近油輪，其後逃到了印尼的[[巴淡島|巴淡島]]，印尼海軍也在6月21日發現了這艘拖船<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/news/asia/south-east-asia/story/13-people-involved-hijacking-malaysian-oil-tanker-orkim-harmony-5-st|title=13 people involved in hijacking of Malaysian oil tanker Orkim Harmony, 5 still at large|publisher=The Straits Times|date=22 June 2015|accessdate=22 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626143400/http://www.straitstimes.com/news/asia/south-east-asia/story/13-people-involved-hijacking-malaysian-oil-tanker-orkim-harmony-5-st|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.asiaone.com/news/malaysia/hijackers%E2%80%99-tugboat-found|title=Hijackers’ tugboat found|author=Joseph Kaos Jr|work=The Star/[[Asia_News_Network|Asia News Network]]|publisher=[[AsiaOne|AsiaOne]]|date=23 June 2015|accessdate=23 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150624041856/http://news.asiaone.com/news/malaysia/hijackers%E2%80%99-tugboat-found|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

